        <num>CC 44</num>
        <heading>44.  Change of domicile</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 44.  Change of domicile
Domicile is maintained until acquisition of a new domicile.  A natural person changes domicile when he moves his residence to another location with the intent to make that location his habitual residence.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
